column1: SELECT productOrServiceCode, fiscal_year, SUM(obligatedAmount) as annual_amount FROM fpds_award3_sunlight WHERE TRIM(UPPER(extentCompeted)) NOT IN ('A', 'F', 'CDO') AND ((TRIM(principalNAICSCode)='') AND (TRIM(UPPER(productOrServiceCode)) IN ('AK', 'AK10', 'AK11', 'AK12', 'AK13', 'AK14', 'AK15', 'AK16', 'AK17', 'B545', 'C116', 'E161', 'E163', 'E169', 'M161', 'M163', 'M169', 'R116', 'R545', 'X161', 'X163', 'X169', 'Y161', 'Y163', 'Y169', 'Z161', 'Z163', 'Z169')))  GROUP BY productOrServiceCode, fiscal_year;
